data.enText: a large round vegetable with thick orange skin. The seeds can be dried and eaten and the soft flesh can be cooked as a vegetable or in sweet pies .

data.chText: 南瓜馅饼是美国传统的感恩节食物。
data.enText: Pumpkin pie is a traditional American dish served on Thanksgiving.

tr: usually large pulpy deep-yellow round fruit of the squash family maturing in late summer or early autumn
a coarse vine widely cultivated for its large pulpy round orange fruit with firm orange skin and numerous seeds
subspecies of Cucurbita pepo include the summer squashes and a few autumn squashes

value.def: A pumpkin is a large, round, orange vegetable with a thick skin.

example.ex: Quarter the pumpkin and remove the seeds.
